      "writtenOn": "2019-10-10T18:55:35Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thanks.\n\nRe. feedback:\n+ The realm is in the proto itself? I don\u0027t see it... Or as request metadata?\n+ This was meant for more general use of writing invocations, not just invocations-from-swarming, in which case general invocations might want updateToken. Won\u0027t the functionality otherwise have a lot of overlap?",
